    <h2>üí° Key Insights</h2>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Constraints enable better performance</strong> ‚Äî not freedom, but structure</li>
        <li><strong>Split tasks:</strong> initializer (setup) + worker (execution) pattern</li>
        <li><strong>Remove anti-laziness prompts</strong> ‚Äî they cause runaway thinking in Claude 4.6+</li>
        <li><strong>Hybrid memory:</strong> hot path (session) + warm path (SQLite) + cold path (vector)</li>
        <li><strong>Trust is earned</strong> ‚Äî transparency &gt; capability</li>
    </ul>

